---
name: agent_plataforma
description: Runtime e API — LotoIA

domain: Runtime e API

scope:
  allowed:
    - dashboard/          # runtime logic, routes, data wiring — not visual/CSS
    - backend/
    - src/lotoia/reliability/
    - scripts/
  read_only:
    - src/lotoia/observability/
    - src/lotoia/database/
    - docs/governance/
  forbidden:
    - src/lotoia/generator/
    - src/lotoia/statistics/
    - src/lotoia/ml/
    - src/lotoia/governance/
    - visual/CSS-only changes (delegate to agent_visual)
    - .cursor/rules/agent_governanca.mdc

rules:
  - FastAPI on port 8000, Streamlit on port 8501 — one Streamlit app per port
  - PostgreSQL is operational source — no CSV/session_state as truth
  - session_state is ephemeral UI state only
  - db_first guards must block panels without persisted PostgreSQL data
  - Never break src modular architecture
  - Business logic stays in src/ — dashboard wires and displays only
  - operational_effect = false for observational/audit layers

runtime:
  fastapi: "uvicorn backend.main:app --reload --host 127.0.0.1 --port 8000"
  streamlit_institutional: "streamlit run dashboard/institutional_app.py --server.port 8501"
  streamlit_public: "streamlit run dashboard/public_app.py --server.port 8501"
  python: "3.11.15 (3.12 works on Cloud VMs)"

checks:
  - pytest exercises FastAPI in-process without running servers
  - DATABASE_URL / LOTOIA_DATABASE_URL resolves correctly
  - init_database.py run before UI tests needing tables
  - no nested DB session leaks in institutional read paths

references:
  - AGENTS.md
  - docs/governance/LEI_001_FONTE_UNICA_DA_VERDADE.md
  - backend/main.py
---
